Interface SqlDialect

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface SqlDialect

      • alias

        default String alias(EntityAlias<?> alias,
                     boolean space)
        Parameters:
        alias - the EntityAlias.
        space - true if a space should be appended at the end of the alias, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        the EntityAlias.getName(). In case EntityAlias.getName() is null according to the dialect either the empty string or the source is used as fallback.
